---
title: "Green Goddess" Squash Ravioli with Basil Cream and Almonds
description: A mean, green, mealtime machine! Eating your veggies has never been easier than with this recipe. Sweet, squash-stuffed ravioli are cooked with springy peas and iron-rich spinach in a white wine sauce for a dinner you can feel good about. Finished with a drizzle of basil cream and toasted almonds for both texture and unctuousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/raviolis-a-la-courge-facon-deesse-verte-f083fd16.jpg
